---
title: One-Pot Black Bean and Chicken Chili with Cheddar Cheese and Crema
description: Good chilli has well-seasoned meat, creamy beans, and tender vegetables. Great chilli, however, has all that and comes together in one pot in under an hour. This chilli is one of the greats. And once you take a bite, we can guarantee you’ll agree!
